    • Field Detail

      • RADIX_FACTORS

        static final int[][] RADIX_FACTORS
        Factors of numbers 2, ..., 36. For 2 <= radix <= 36, RADIX_FACTORS[radix] contains an array of integers containing the different factors of the radix.
